gs:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- Content for level 400+<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- Manarune fix<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New items, crafting<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New monsters<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New quests<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- Rebalance<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New land<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New NPCs<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New tasks<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- Item shop changes<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- Addon doll instead of Addoner NPC<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- New level rewards<\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" font-size-adjust:=\"\" none;=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" auto;=\"\" font-variant-alternates:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-ligatures:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-position:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" normal;\"=\"\">- Dice game limits modified<\/p>","date":"1702868698","name":"admin"},{"id":"7","title":"","text":"<div>As the pace of the game exceeded my <b>every expectation<\/b>, a lot of problems I didn't realize came to the surface.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>From now on, potions and runes do not run out after use.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>EKs can use strong mana potions from now aswell.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Manarune will be slightly boosted.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Supreme health potion is boosted.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>All experience rewards from higher level monsters and bosses (!) are nerfed and will be nerfed even harder, due to players reaching levels I never even dreamed of in all my expectations.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>As this is a solo project that he has been preparing for months, it is extremely difficult to deliver a product that will be free of bugs, including some extremely stupid ones.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>At this point I can only say sorry, I did my best to make the game on Mythoria a lot of fun for everyone, at the same time a huge thank you to every person who has played, is playing and possibly will continue to play.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Although this mess is huge and hard to clean up, I'm not going to let go and as many fixes will be added to the game as needed.<\/div>","date":"1702789039","name":"admin"},{"id":"6","title":"","text":"<div>Here's a little guide to the most commonly used basic spells, spells for post-promotion vocations and a quick overview of Land of Misery.<br><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><a href=\"https:\/\/mythoria.gitbook.io\/mythoriaguide\/\">https:\/\/mythoria.gitbook.io\/mythoriaguide\/<\/a><br><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Join official Discord and get your free item shop points!<\/div><div><a href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/etQSB7GkRC\" title=\"Discord\" target=\"\">https:\/\/discord.gg\/etQSB7GkRC<\/a><br><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Follow us on TikTok too!<\/div><div><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tiktok.com\/@mythoria.online\">https:\/\/www.tiktok.com\/@mythoria.online<\/a><br><\/div>","date":"1702740792","name":"admin"},{"id":"5","title":"","text":"<div>Server will stay closed until official launch, <b>December 16, 21:00 UTC+1.&nbsp;<\/b><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>AoL has been removed from the item shop, we are staying with the NO AoLs policy, you can only get them from a very high level quest or from fishing with a mechanical rod.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>I am aware of a bug with some houses, whereby they cannot be purchased and can be entered like any other room.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>I have done my best to make Mythoria as polished as possible, but as this is a solo project, I do not exclude many imperfections.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>All of them will be corrected and all player suggestions will be considered on an ongoing basis.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>At the moment I invite you to create an account and create a character, if you are able to, invite some friends, the more players the better.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The development of Mythoria does not end on opening day.<\/div>","date":"1702676971","name":"admin"},{"id":"4","title":"","text":"We just uploaded a <b>trailer<\/b> where you can get a glimpse of what Mythoria looks like! Check it now!<div><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=7TQQbhbtFQ8\">https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=7TQQbhbtFQ8<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We've also added <b>30 new items <\/b>to the fishing boxes and mythical stone boxes. More randomness.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div style=\"orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><b>New spells<\/b> list :&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/mythoria.gitbook.io\/mythoriaguide\/new-spells\">https:\/\/mythoria.gitbook.io\/mythoriaguide\/new-spells<\/a><\/div><div><i><b><br><\/b><\/i><\/div><div><\/div>","date":"1702651196","name":"admin"},{"id":"2","title":"","text":"<a href=\"https:\/\/mythoria.online\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" data-proxy-href=\"\/proxy.php?link=https%3A%2F%2Fmythoria.online&amp;hash=e804659d9b48d0a12f03ad4d9be5a0be\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Mythoria<\/a><span segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"fira=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"droid=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(254,=\"\" 254,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(20, 20, 20); color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\">&nbsp;will launch on 16\/12\/2023 21:00 UTC+1.&nbsp;<\/span><br><div><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(20, 20, 20); color: rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family: \" segoe=\"\" ui\"